====Noun====
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} The [[state]] of reduced [[consciousness]] during which a human or [[animal]] rests in a daily rhythm.
#: ''I really need some '''sleep'''''.
#: ''We need to conduct an overnight '''sleep''' test to diagnose your '''sleep''' problem.''
# {{context|countable|informal|lang=en}} An act or instance of sleeping.
#: ''I’m just going to have a quick '''sleep'''''.
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} [[rheum|Rheum]] found in the corner of the eyes after waking, whether real or a figurative objectification of sleep (in the sense of ''reduced consciousness'').
#: ''Wipe the '''sleep''' from your eyes''.

